name: Appetizer Sampler
description: Our most popular appetizer. Ground beef nachos, shredded chicken quesadillas, and chicken flautas garnished with guacamole, sour cream and jalapenos on a bed of lettuce. No substitutions please.

name: Queso
description: A cheesy Tex-Mex Staple!

name: Nachos
description: A Tex Mex favorite! Tortilla chips covered with homemade refried beans, Monterrey jack cheese and cheddar cheese. Garnished with lettuce, jalapeños, guacamole, and sour cream.
modifier: Substitute ground beef or shredded chicken.

name: Quesadillas
description: A large flour tortilla buttered and stuffed with mixed cheeses, Tomatoes, chives, and your choice of fajita steak or chicken breast. Garnished with lettuce guacamole, and sour cream.

name: Queso Fundido
description: Mixed cheeses, fresh Pico do Gallo, grilled bell pepper, and your choice of fajita steak, chicken, set ABLAZE at your table by server. Served with flour tortillas.

name: Seven Layer Dip
description: A scrumptious bowl of layered dips! Our queso mixed with cheese, refried beans, and ground beef topped with guacamole, sour cream and jalapeños.

name: Mexican Shrimp Cocktail
description: Tasty shrimp tossed in homemade Mexican cocktail sauce with cilantro, pico de gallo, and fresh avacado. Served with extra crunchy flour tortilla chips.

name: Fajita Salad
description: A fresh bed of chopped lettuce topped with your choice fajita steak or chicken and completed with diced tomatoes, bell peppers and cheddar cheese. Comes with your choice of dressing.

name: Sizzling Grilled Salad
description: Fresh chopped lettuce, carrot strips, red cabbage, mixed cheeses, sliced avocados and tomato wedges completed at your table with sizzling fajita steak or chicken and grilled onions.

name: Taco Salad
description: A large taco bowl shell filled with chopped lettuce, diced tomatoes, mixed cheese and topped with your choice of ground beef, shredded chicken. Garnished with tortilla strips, fresh guacamole, and a side of dressing.

name: Tortilla Soup
description: A Frijoles staple. Sure to warm your bones right up.

name: Tacos al Carbon
description: Three rolled flour tortillas filled with diced fajita steak or juicy chicken breast and garnished with shredded cheddar cheese, Pico de Gallo and fresh guacamole.

name: Street Tacos
description: Three corn tortillas filled with slow roasted shredded beef (Barbacoa) or seasoned pulled pork (Carnitas), topped with fresh cilantro and chopped white onions. Garnished with fresh lime wedges, fired-roasted salsa and guacamole.

name: Fish Tacos
description: Three soft flour tortillas filled with our specially seasoned Tilapia, shredded lettuce, chives and Pico de Gallo. Garnished with fresh lemon wedges and a side of creamy cilantro sauce.

name: Shrimp Tacos
description: Three soft flour tortillas filled with garlic butter pan seared shrimp and topped with lettuce, Pico de Gallo and a slice of avocado. Garnished with a side of fire-roasted salsa.

name: Taco Dinner
description: Three tacos (soft or crispy) filled with lettuce, tomatoes, and cheddar cheese with your choice of shredded chicken or ground beef.

name: Fajitas
description: A Mexican classic! Tender marinated steak, juicy chicken breast, pulled pork, susage or a combination of two served on top of a bed of sizzling onions and bell peppers. Complimented with diced tomatoes.

name: Triple Meat Fajitas
description: Our classic fajitas with an extra helping of meat. Choose three different meats (Steak, Chicken, Shrimp, Susage, or pulled pork) and we'll served them on top of a bed of sizzling onions and bell peppers with diced tomatoes on top.

name: Shrimp Fajitas
description: Tasty jumbo shrimp sautéed in garlic butter and served on top of a bed of sizzling onions and bell peppers, a scrumptious twist on a classic.

name: Fajitas for Two
description: A double portion of our classic fajitas (Steak, chicken, pulled pork, susage or a combination of 2) on one big sizzling skillet.

name: Enchilada Dinner
description: Mix and match your favorite three enchiladas and sauces. Choose from: cheese, seasoned ground beef, seasoned shredded chicken, or fresh spinach.

name: Supreme Enchilada Dinner
description: Two rolled corn tortillas filled with your choice of: barbacoa, carnitas, fajita steak, shrimp, or chicken then covered in your favorite sauce(s). Garnished with fresh guacamole.

name: Enchilada-Fajita Montada
description: Two classic cheese enchiladas smothered in queso and topped with your choice of either: diced steak and grilled onions or diced chicken and sautéed mushrooms.

name: Flauta Dinner
description: Three rolled flour tortillas stuffed with cheese and filled with your choice fajita steak or chicken, then deep-fried until crispy. Garnished with guacamole, sour cream and queso.

name: Tamale Dinner
description: A Tex-Mex staple! Two of our giant homemade beef Tamales, served with a cup chili con carne that is garnished with shredded cheese chives and diced tomatoes.

name: Chile Rellenos
description: Battered stuffed poblano pepper filled with mixed cheese and your choice of: ground beef, shredded chicken or extra cheese and covered in ranchero sauce.

name: Burrito Grande Dinner
description: One beast of a burrito! A large flour tortilla stuffed with refried beans, cheese and your choice of meat, then covered with your favorite sauce. (Queso, Chile, Sour Cream, Verde, or Ranchero)

name: Chimichanga Dinner
description: Crispy goodness! A large flour tortilla, filled with Mexican rice, mixed cheese and your choice of meat, rolled then deep-fried until golden brown and smothered in creamy queso sauce.

name: Mini Chimichangas Dinner
description: A Frijoles favorite! Three mini chimis, a shredded chicken chimi covered in sour cream sauce, a ground beef chimi covered in chile con carne, and a cheese chimi covered in queso.

name: Vera Cruz Combination Platter
description: Two beef enchiladas covered in chili con carne sauce and paired with a crispy beef taco.

name: Cozumel Combination Platter
description: Two beef enchiladas covered in chili con carne sauce, a crispy beef taco and a tostada.

name: Acapulco Combination Platter
description: A ground beef enchilada covered in chili con carne, a crispy beef taco, a cheese chili relleno covered in ranchero salsa, and ground beef tostada make this a Frijoles favorite.

name: Durango Combination Platter
description: A real sampler platter. A cheese enchilada covered in queso, a chicken enchilada covered in sour cream sauce, a cheese chile relleno covered in ranchero sauce and a ground beef tostada.

name: Rio Grande
description: A tostada with four bacon wrapped shrimp stuffed with jack cheese and poblano pepper paired with your choice of enchilada smothered in your favorite sauce.

name: Yucatan
description: Our fresh Cajun seasoned grilled tilapia fillet served over a bed of Mexican rice and paired with four jumbo shrimp sautéed on garlic butter. Garnished with fresh lemon wedges.

name: Grilled Tilapia
description: Seasoned grilled tilapia fillet served over a bed of Mexican rice and garnished with fresh lemon wedges.

name: Pollo Boracho
description: A juicy grilled chicken breast covered in our house mushroom white zinfandel borracho sauce.

name: Steak Mar y Tierra
description: A juicy marinated top round steak covered in ranchero sauce with mixed cheese melted on top. Paired with four jumbo shrimp sautéed in garlic butter.

name: Chicken Mar y Tierra
description: A juicy marinated chicken breast covered in creamy cilantro sauce and pico with mixed cheeses melted on top, paired with four jumbo shrimp sautéed in garlic butter.

name: Carne Asada
description: A marinated top round steak topped with grilled onions and paired alongside a cheese enchilada with chili con carne sauce on top. Pollo Asada also available.

name: Brochetas de Camaron
description: Six jumbo bacon wrapped shrimp stuffed with mixed cheese and poblano pepper served with garlic butter sauce.

name: Arroz con Pollo
description: Strips of tender chicken breast on top of a bed of rice and smothered in our chili con queso sauce completed with a cup of tortilla soup.

name: Pollo Adobe
description: Strips of grilled chicken breast with sautéed onions, bell peppers and mushrooms covered in our creamy cilantro sauce.

name: Mesquite Grilled Chicken
description: A healthy choice. A juicy, marinated chicken breast mesquite grilled to perfection.

name: Steak Ranchero
description: A choice cut steak, char-grilled to your liking and topped with ranchero salsa then, paired with a cheese enchilada smothered in chili con carne sauce.

name: Fountain Drink
description: Coke, Sprite, Diet Coke, Dr. Pepper, Barq's Root Beer,  Minute Maid Lemonade.

name: Iced Tea
description: Fresh brewed tea available in unsweetened and sweetend.

name: Hot Coffee
description: Fresh brewed Community brand hot coffee.

name: Bottled Mexican Soft Drink
description: Coke or Orange Fanta.

name: Bottled Jarritos
description: Guava, Lime, Pineapple, Mandarin

name: Topo Chico
description: 12oz Glass Bottle

name: Brownie Sundae
description: Tasty walnut brownie topped with vanilla ice cream, drizzled chocolate sauce, whipped cream and a cherry on top.

name: Caramel Flan
description: Creamy caramel custard topped with whipped cream and a cherry.

name: Fried Ice Cream
description: Deep fried vanilla ice cream coated in crispy corn flakes, drizzled with chocolate sauce, wipped cream and a cherry. Served with cinnamon flour chips.

name: Cinnamon Sugar Churros ala Mode
description: Delicious cinnamon sugar bavarian cream filled churros, drizzled with chocolate sauce. Served alongside vanilla ice cream, and whipped topping.

name: Cheesecake Chimichanga
description: A deep fried pastry filled with New York style cheesecake, strawberry sauce and dusted with cinnimon sugar.

name: Sopapillas
description: Six sweet Mexican pastries dusted with cinnamon sugar, served with honey and butter.

name: Queso
description: A cheesy Tex-Mex Staple!

name: Quesadillas
description: A large flour tortilla buttered and stuffed with mixed cheeses, Tomatoes, chives, and your choice of fajita steak or chicken breast. Garnished with lettuce guacamole, and sour cream.

name: Supreme Nachos
description: Cripy corn tortillas covered in homemade refried beans, mixed cheese and your choice of seasoned ground beef or shredded chicken. Garnished with chopped lettuce, picked jalepenos, sour cream and fresh guacamole.

name: Fajita Nachos
description: Cripy corn tortillas covered in homemade refried beans, mixed cheese and your choice of marinated flame grilled steak or juicy mesquite grilled chicken. Garnished with chopped lettuce, picked jalepenos, sour cream and fresh guacamole.

name: Lunch Sampler
description: Ground beef nachos, shredded chicken quesadillas, and a chicken flauta farnished with chopped lettuce, pickled jalepenos, sour cream, and fresh guacamole.

name: 2 Item Combo
description: Choose 2 of the following: cheese enchilada, ground beef enchilada, shredded chicken enchilada, spinach enchilada, soft beef taco, crispy beef taco, soft shredded chicken taco, or crispy shredded chicken taco.

name: Taco Salad
description: A large taco bowl shell filled with chopped lettuce, diced tomatoes, and shredded cheddar cheese, topped with your choice of seasoned ground beef or shredded chicken. Garnished with crispy tortilla strips, fresh guacamole and you favorite salad dressing.

name: Lunch Fajita Salad
description: Juicy strips of fajita steak or chicken on top of chopped lettuce, diced tomatoes and shredded cheddar chesse.

name: Chile Relleno
description: A battered poblano pepper filled with cheese that is deep fried and smothered in ranchero sauce.
modifier: Add Ground Beef or Shredded Chicken

name: Lunch Fajitas
description: Tender marinated steak, juicy chicken breast, pulled pork or susage on top of a bed of sizzling onions, bell peppers and topped with diced tomatoes. Garnished with guacamole, and pico de gallo.

name: Lunch Acapulco
description: A cheese chile relleno covered in ranchero sauce, a crispy beef taco, and a beef tostada.

name: Fish Tacos
description: Two soft tacos filled with seasoned Tilapia, shredded lettuce, pico de gallo and green onions. Garnished with fresh lemon wedges and a side of creamy cilantro sauce.

name: Lunch Supreme Enchiladas
description: Two rolled corned tortillas, filled with your choice of barbacoa, carnitas, fajita steak, or fajita chicken and smothered in queso.

name: Lunch Durango
description: A chile cheese rello covered in ranchero sauce, chicken enchilada smothered in sour cream sauce, and a beef tostada.

name: Chimichanga
description: A large flour tortilla, filled with Mexican rice, mixed cheese and your choice of meat, rolled then deep-fried until golden brown and smothered in creamy queso sauce.

name: Arroz con Pollo
description: Strips of tender chicken breast on top of a bed of rice and smothered in our chili con queso sauce completed with a cup of tortilla soup.
